com.easydataservices.db2admintool.util.parser

Class CommandOutputParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.easydataservices.db2admintool.util.parser.CommandOutputParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Parser

    public abstract class CommandOutputParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract base class for parsing command output. Subclasses extended this class to provide parsing support for the output of specific commands.
    Version:
    2021.12.11

      • parse

        public java.util.List<?> parse()
        Parse all command output. Invokes method parseAll(), implemented by the subclass, and returns results from that method. If the stream is not fully consumed by parseAll then parse reads and discard all remaining data.
